  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Executive - Institutions</strong></p>\n<p>Singapore Asia Publishers, a leading provider of educational assessment books in Singapore, is seeking a dynamic and enthusiastic Institutional Sales Executive to join our team. This role is integral to our mission of delivering high-quality educational resources to schools, teachers, and students in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>- Develop an in-depth understanding of our extensive range of educational assessment books, including content, unique selling points, and target audiences.</p>\n<p>- Build and maintain relationships with schools and teachers, understanding their needs and recommending suitable books and resources.</p>\n<p>- Actively promote our books through presentations, meetings, and events, ensuring our products meet the educational needs of our customers.</p>\n<p>- Stay informed about market trends, competitors, and customer feedback to identify new opportunities and improve our product offerings.</p>\n<p>- Assist customers with placing orders, ensure timely delivery, and handle any post-sales inquiries or issues.</p>\n<p>- Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets, contributing to the overall growth of the company.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Diploma and above</p>\n<p>- At least 2 years of sales experience preferrably in similar industry.</p>\n<p>- Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</p>\n<p>- A passion for education and helping students succeed.</p>\n<p>- Self-motivated with a proactive approach to sales.</p>\n<p>- Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Please write in with full resume to sharonyoo@sapgrp.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please send in your resume to sharonyoo@sapgrp.com</p>\n<p>Salary will commensurate with experience.</p>\n<p>Job Types: Full-time, Part-time, Contract, Internship, Freelance</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Salary will commensurate with working experience in relevant industry.</p>",
